# Mypackage

Mypackage is a Python library for sorting lists or array like objects in descending order by top ```n```.

## Installation

Use the package manager [pip](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/) to install mypackage.

```bash
pip install mypackage
```

## Usage

```python
import mypackage

# returns [8, 7, 4]
top_n([8, 3, 2, 7, 4], 3)

# returns [8, 7, 4]
top_n([8, 0, -1, 7, 4], 3)
    assert myModule.

# returns [12, 10]
top_n([10, 1, 12, 9, 2], 2)
```

